<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset - Equalmint</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7fb;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 26px;
            color: #10b981;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .header img {
            max-width: 120px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #444444;
        }

        .reset-button {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #10b981;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .reset-button:hover {
            background-color: #059669;
        }

        .warning {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .warning p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888888;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
            padding-top: 10px;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #10b981;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .social-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .social-links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #10b981;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="/assets/logo.png" alt="Equalmint Logo">
            <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password for your Equalmint account.</p>
            <p>Click the button below to reset your password. This link will expire in 15 minutes.</p>

            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
                <a href="<%= resetLink %>" class="reset-button">Reset Password</a>
            </p>

            <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #10b981; font-size: 14px;"><%= resetLink %></p>

            <div class="warning">
                <p><strong>⚠️ Security Notice:</strong> If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
            </div>

            <p>For security reasons, this link will expire in 15 minutes.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>
                The Equalmint Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Equalmint. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>For more information, visit our <a href="https://app.equalmint.com">website</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="social-links">
            <p>Follow us on:</p>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/Equalmint">Twitter</a>
            <a href="https://facebook.com/Equalmint">Facebook</a>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/company/Equalmint">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

